Package: earthquakeDC
Type: Package
Title: Package for visualization of NOAA earthquakes
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Dorothy", "Chen", email = "xiuqic2008@gmail.com",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Dorothy Chen <xiuqic2008@gmail.com>
Depends:
    R (>= 3.2.2)
Description: This package is built for cleaning and visualizing NOAA
     earthquake data. It is able to create earthquake timelines and uses leaflet
     maps to show earthquake locations.
LazyData: TRUE
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
Imports:
     dplyr,
     ggplot2,
     leaflet,
     lubridate,
     scales,
     stringr
Suggests:
     knitr,
     rmarkdown,
     testthat,
     readr
